      '<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-size: 20px; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">About this listing</h2><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Discover the ultimate fly-in getaway at the Cabin Creek Log Cabin in Montana! You can land your own plane at the Cabin Creek Landing Airport and park on the property steps away from the cabin (We have our own apron and tiedowns), making this a dream retreat for aviation enthusiasts. With Glacier National Park nearby, enjoy breathtaking views, modern amenities, and the convenience of having your airplane right at your doorstep. Whether you’re looking for a peaceful escape or an adventure-filled vacation, this cabin offers a one-of-a-kind experience.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Enjoy the beautiful scenery, airstrip on your front porch, and many lakes&nbsp; within the area, A hour Drive to Whitefish Mountain or Blacktail Ski Hill. When you stay at this beautiful little log cabin retreat on a&nbsp; 3-acre lot!&nbsp; It features a one-bedroom loft with a queen bed,&nbsp; a full bathroom, and an additional bunkhouse 50ft. away with two (2) single cots, power, and a heater.&nbsp; This rustic modern cabin has everything, including a wood fireplace.&nbsp; This is the perfect stop for your Glacier Park Gateway on your way to all the famous surrounding airstrips. Kitchen is well equiped with all the basic condiments.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">The Hilltop Hitchin Post Restaruant and Gas Station are within 2 miles.&nbsp; &nbsp;Fly into Kalsipell&nbsp; City Airport S27 (16NM)&nbsp; for all your grocery needs(Grocery store is adjacent to plane parking) and car rentals and fuel at Red Eagle FBO<span>&nbsp;</span><a href="https://redeagleaviation.com/" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(175, 35, 34); text-decoration: none; transition: 0.2s;">Red Eagle Aviation – Your Gateway To Sky-High Adventures | Kalispell, MT</a>.&nbsp; TV with DVD’s. No WIFI</p><ul class="detail-list detail-list-2-cols" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; list-style: none; columns: 2; color: rgb(59, 66, 73); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><li class="additional-informationf654b8b83c8b89" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 400; text-transform: capitalize; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif;">Additional Information:<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-weight: 700;">Couch in living area, Stairs to loft are steep Hanger can be made available.</strong></li></ul>',
